{"id": "1418008141232078990", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "589115953355423805", "author_name": "magushermes", "author_bot": false, "content": "另外，我其實無法理解的一點是：依照星辰篇第三章這樣講，威廉等於是在亞蘭沙漠遇害的當下就被動地撕裂次元傳到密斯卡托尼克世界耶？！是這樣嗎？！", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T22:58:06.187000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
